snippet.textDisplay:
Already in pain as a neophyte to spicy food, he takes a huge bite of that awful Da Bomb wing, gets Da Smashed in the face hard, looks like he's going to wave the white flag ... That impassioned, focused "fuck you, dude" as he pulls himself back and devours the rest is the quintessential "The Hot Ones" moment for me.  

What a great episode, in so many ways. At the moment, it feels like the best (but LaBeouf, ... Ramsey, ... Rudd, ...) - one for the time capsule for sure.
